    <note>Zhang(2) Pin [342] His ancestors were Yuzhang jun Zhang(2), who  moved to Jianning, Pucheng xian. Pin's father, Guzhe [3185], was jinshi number one under the Southern Tang. His son, Fang [3184], Jie(3)'s [345] father, was a military officer. Zhang(2) Dexiang [344] was collateral kin of Pin's generation of Pucheng xian Zhang(2). XCB, 93.11b, 110.10a, 113.3b, 12b; Guangxi TZ, 16.7b; SS, 301.9b-10a. CBD, 3, 2085.</note>
